Document: ClassJointLimitationCone3D
Path: godot/classes/class_jointlimitationcone3d.rst
Summary: A cone-shaped joint limitation constraint for 3D skeletal animations, used with ChainIK3D.

A cone shape limitation that interacts with ChainIK3D. This constraint restricts joint movement within a conical volume, commonly used in inverse kinematics systems to maintain natural limb motion ranges. The cone's orientation and angle determine the permissible movement area for the constrained joint.
